: "نَتَجْنا", "in_corpus": false, "count": null, "asp": "p", "per": "1", "gen": "m", "num": "p"}, {"role": "past_1ms", "form": "نَتَجْتُ", "in_corpus": true, "count": 1, "asp": "p", "per": "1", "gen": "m", "num": "s"}], "frequency_in_corpus": 4, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["verb"], "has_etymology": false, "sense_count": 4}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n39271"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E"}}, "translations": {"en": "to bear young", "fa": "زایمان دادن", "ur": "بچہ دینا", "tr": "doğum yaptırmak", "id": "melahirkan", "bn": "প্রসব করা", "es": "dar a luz", "fr": "mettre bas", "de": "gebären", "ru": "приносить приплод", "zh": "产仔"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to bear, to bring forth (young)"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to ensue, to result"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to derive, to proceed"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be generated"}]}, "etymology": null, "ipa": ["/na.ta.d͡ʒa/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n39271", "headword_ar": "نَتَجَ", "root": "ntj", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K, &c.,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (as in the L, [but I believe this to be a mistake,]) or"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (accord. to the Msb, MS, MF,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "natojN", "text_ar": "نَتْجٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Antj", "text_ar": "انتج", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (A;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He assisted"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a she-camel, (S, K, &c.,) [and a mare, see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nutijato", "text_ar": "نُتِجَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",] and a ewe or she-goat (Msb) [or other quadruped],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in bringing forth; delivered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "her"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of her young one; acting to her as a midwife does to a woman."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, Msb, &c.) The original form of expression is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "natajahaA waladFA", "text_ar": "نَتَجَهَا وَلَدًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He assisted her in bringing forth a young one; delivered her of a young one."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) El-Kumeyt has used the form ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ainotataja", "text_ar": "اِنْتَتَجَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the sense of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nataja", "text_ar": "نَتَجَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": but it is not commonly current in Arabic. (TA.) AHn mentions the saying"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~aAsu", "text_ar": "النَّاسُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_i*aA naA='ati Aljabohapu nat~aju", "text_ar": "اـِذَا نَا=ءَتِ الجَبْهَةُ نَتَّجُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wawal~aduwA waA@jotuniYa A^aw~alu AlkamoA^api", "text_ar": "وَوَلَّدُوا وَا@جْتُنِىَ اَوَّلُ الكَمْاَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "When El-Jebhah"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(the tenth of the Mansions of the Moon)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sets antiheliacally,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(for the setting, not the rising, is here meant, and this it did, about the commencement of the era of the Flight, in central Arabia, on the 11th of February,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the people assist their beasts, much,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "frequently, in bringing forth, and deliver them, and the first of the truffles are gathered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. Thus he relates the saying, with teshdeed to the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "v", "text_ar": "ث"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ntj", "text_ar": "نتج"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", to denote frequency of the act. (L.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nutijato", "text_ar": "نُتِجَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", pass. in form, [but neut. in signification,] inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nitaAjN", "text_ar": "نِتَاجٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, &c.) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tanojN", "text_ar": "تَنْجٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (TA;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^unotijato", "text_ar": "اُنْتِجَتْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) also pass. in form; and some say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "natajato", "text_ar": "نَتَجَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", but this is rare, and not heard by IAar; (TA;) and some, also, say ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^anotajato", "text_ar": "اَنْتَجَتْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Lth, Kr,) but Az holds this to be a mistake; (TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel, IAar, S, K, &c., and a mare, IAar, and a sheep or goat or other quadruped, Msb)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "brought forth:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, Msb, TA:) or one does not say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nutijati Al$~aApu", "text_ar": "نُتِجَتِ الشَّاةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "unless a man assist at the bringing forth. (Lth.) Thus one suppresses the objective complement of the verb. And one also says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tunijati Aln~aAqapu waladFA", "text_ar": "تُنِجَتِ النَّاقَةُ وَلَدًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The she-camel brought forth a young one:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and in like manner one says of a ewe or a she-goat: and sometimes, with the same meaning,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "natajati AlnAqp wldA", "text_ar": "نَتَجَتِ الناقة ولدا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the act. form. (Msb.) One also says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA_ibilu", "text_ar": "الاـِبِلُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tanaAtajati", "text_ar": "تَنَاتَجَتِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The camels brought forth."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) [You say,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nataja Alqawomu", "text_ar": "نَتَجَ القَوْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Lth,) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^anotaja", "text_ar": "اَنْتَجَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (L,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The people's camels"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sheep"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "goats brought forth:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Lth, L:) or ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^anotajuwA", "text_ar": "اَنْتَجُوا", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "they had pregnant camels bringing forth."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) One may also say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nutija Alwaladu", "text_ar": "نُتِجَ الوَلَدُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The young one"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a she-camel &c., [see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nutijato", "text_ar": "نُتِجَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", above,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was brought forth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "born."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) See 4. ―         -b3-  [Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alr~iyHu tunotiju Als~aHaAba", "text_ar": "الرِّيحُ تُنْتِجُ السَّحَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wind assists the clouds in the discharging of their rain;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "draws forth the rain from the clouds."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, L.) ―         -b4-  ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nutija", "text_ar": "نُتِجَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It was produced, it resulted,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was a natural consequence."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}], "source_refs": ["Msb", "K", "Lth", "Kr", "T", "TA", "L"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}